items.sentence: I knew that Tom had never actually done that.
I knew that Tom had already tried to do that.
I knew that Tom didn't want to do that today.
I knew that Tom didn't want to do that alone.
I know Tom isn't going to do that by himself.
I know Tom isn't going to be able to do that.
I know Tom isn't getting tired of doing that.
I know Tom is the only one who can't do that.
I know Tom is still interested in doing that.
I know Tom is going to find out who did that.
